OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK scraps rich foreign     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finvestor visa scheme       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Visas offering foreign investors       
OL,6, fast-track residency in the UK are     
OL,7, being scrapped with immediate effect,  
OL,8, the home secretary has confirmed.      
OL,10,FPriti Patel said ending Tier 1 investor
OL,11,Fvisas, for those spending at least #2m,
OL,12,Fwas the start of a "renewed crackdown  
OL,13,Fon illicit finance and fraud".         
OL,15,FThe scheme was introduced in 2008 to   
OL,16,Fencourage wealthy people from outside  
OL,17,Fthe EU to invest in the UK.            
OL,19,FIt has been under review for some time,
OL,20,Fafter concerns it is open to abuse.    
